- descriptor
- metadata
- tags
- CTA

## 15.3 Compact utility card
Used for:
- quick links
- support actions
- member actions
- small featured lists

## 15.4 Proof/testimonial card
Used for:
- client outcomes
- result snapshots
- social proof

## 15.5 Pricing card
Used only on membership pricing and occasional comparison blocks.

